OL,3,CBakers share secret to 70 years of
OL,4,Cmarriage
OL,6,FA couple on the Isle of Man say
OL,7,F'honesty and forgiveness' are the
OL,8,Fsecret to a long and happy marriage.
OL,9,FAnn, 90, and Jack Kaighin, 91, are
OL,10,Fcelebrating their platinum wedding
OL,11,Fanniversary, after 70 years of
OL,12,Fmarriage.
OL,14,FThe pair got married on March 24, 1956
OL,15,Fat Braddan Church on the outskirts of
OL,16,FDouglas, and now live in Laxey on the
OL,17,Feast coast of the island. They have
OL,18,Ffour children, four grandchildren, and
OL,19,Ftwo great grand-children.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
