FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774357890
OL,3,CBakers share secret to 70 years of
OL,4,Cmarriage
OL,6,FJack said: "We're mystified how we've
OL,7,Fmanaged to get to 70 years being
OL,8,Fmarried!"
OL,10,FAnn said: "It's unbelievable! We've
OL,11,Falways done a lot of different things,
OL,12,Fand I think that's the secret."
OL,14,FJack is a master baker and he and Ann
OL,15,Fran a successful bakery business in
OL,16,FLaxey for 20 years, and he was
OL,17,Fpresident of the island's Federation
OL,18,Fof Master Bakers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774357890
OL,3,CBakers share secret to 70 years of
OL,4,Cmarriage
OL,6,FAs a result of this, he has judged
OL,7,Fmany cake and confectionery
OL,8,Fcompetitions over the years including
OL,9,Fat agricultural shows. In the
OL,10,Fcommunity, he served on Laxey
OL,11,FCommissioners and is the current
OL,12,Fpresident of Lonan Fellowship.
OL,14,FJack and Ann are very knowledgeable
OL,15,Fabout the Isle of Man, and Jack still
OL,16,Fvisits various groups on the island
OL,17,Fpresenting Magic Lantern shows,
OL,18,Fdisplaying past pictures of the
OL,19,Fisland, while Ann was the editor of
OL,20,Fthe IoM Family History Society journal
OL,21,Ffor 20 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774357890
OL,3,CBakers share secret to 70 years of
OL,4,Cmarriage
OL,6,FBoth are qualified Blue Badge guides
OL,7,Fand Ann was a reader and librarian in
OL,8,FDouglas and Onchan libraries for 20
OL,9,Fyears, as well as a leading light in
OL,10,FLaxey Women's Institute for decades.
OL,12,FWhen asked their favourite things
OL,13,Fabout each other, Ann said: "We never
OL,14,Fhold a grievance, because we always
OL,15,Fend up seeing the funny side. And
OL,16,Fbefore you know it you have a cup of
OL,17,Ftea and then it's gone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
