PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774357890
OL,3,CBakers share secret to 70 years of
OL,4,Cmarriage
OL,6,FJack said: "When I met Ann for the
OL,7,Fvery first time, I was head over heels
OL,8,Fwith how very attractive she was, and
OL,9,Fstill is."
OL,11,F"And he always knows how to get out
OL,12,Ffrom under my feet!", Ann added.
OL,14,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
